{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"05a4b018a3","title":"正面教员与反面教员","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4f93c9b9cc","index":0,"year":1965,"month":2,"day":null,"articleId":"05a4b018a3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji47","name":"毛泽东全集第47卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/47-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji47":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2eebc8e35d","type":"title","text":"正面教员与反面教员","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"05a4b018a3"},{"id":"0d606855b2","type":"paragraph","text":"革命的政党，革命的人民，总是要反复地经受正反两个方面的教育，经过比较和对照，才能够锻炼得成熟起来，才有赢得胜利的保证。我们的中国共产党人，有正面教员，这就是马克思、恩格斯、列宁、斯大林。也有反面教员，这就是蒋介石、日本帝国主义者、美帝国主义者和我们党内犯“左”倾或右倾机会主义路线错误的人。如果只有正面教员而没有反面教员，中国革命是不会取得胜利的。轻视反面教员的作用，就不是一个彻底的辩证唯物主义者。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"05a4b018a3"}],"page":{"id":"b758f49adb","publicationId":"maoquanji47","articleId":"05a4b018a3","start":497,"end":497}}}},"__N_SSG":true}